** ER
E-01 TYPE ERROR.< 1 / 2 /  3 /  4 / 5 >
E-02 UPDATE INST IS ERROR <0= CANCEL. 1= CHANGE. 2= ADD>
E-03 MATERIAL CODE IS NOT INPUT.
E-04 THERE IS NOT MATERIAL CODE IN PART INFORMATION M/F.
E-05 MATERIAL PROPERTIES IS NOT INPUT.
E-06
E-07
E-08 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT M/F DOES NOT  EXIST .
E-09 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED, BUT  M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY.
E-10 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT  M/F DOES NOT  EXIST.
E-11 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED, BUT  M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY.
E-12 ADD WAS APPOINTED, BUT  M/F EXIST.
E-13
E-14 QUENCHING TIME IS NOT INPUT.
E-15 TEMPERING TEMPERATURE IS NOT INPUT.
E-16 CO2 IS NOT INPUT.
E-17 HARD STANDARD IS NOT INPUT.
E-18 INPUT ALREADY.
E-19 PASSWORD IS NOT INPUT.
E-20 PASSWORD ERROR
